--- !u!114 &1766915714
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1766915713}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3089b53a39858db4d8673bfadcdc12d5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogBox: {fileID: 1762141775}
  dialogText: {fileID: 1300943634}
  speakerNameText: {fileID: 121795798}
  portraitImage: {fileID: 1288517481}
  portraitFrame: {fileID: 1172073840}
  dark: {fileID: 365560361}
  choice1: {fileID: 1530363298}
  choice2: {fileID: 838602642}
  choice3: {fileID: 314781445}
  background: {fileID: 643133838}
  swap: {fileID: 6073422452625171728, guid: 081190445a90f544d81c6b65611c1dce, type: 3}
  typingSpeed: 0.03
  dialogChunks:
  - text: In the afternoons, your task as King of Sheeps is to make important decisions
      for the wellbeing of your fellow sheep.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Specifically, the afternoons see you make "Yes" or "No" decisions as your
      loyal subjects / S-PAIR classmates confer with you.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: You must balance three core resources... If any of them go the zero, then
      your kingdom is doomed.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: '"Sheep" is the population of your beloved kingdom, affecting too your
      military abilities and overall manpower.'
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: '"Land" is the total area of territory your kingdom spans (measured in
      square meters), which affects the wellbeing of your citizens and the kingdom''s
      ability to prosper.'
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Finally, "Money" is the total amount of money... Pretty self-explanatory.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Each day you'll need to make three decisions...
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: So, let's begin!
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Your majesty, I'd like to purchase a plot of land for me and my family.
      I'll have you know, I'm the greatest grass farmer out there!
    speakerName: Adam
    portrait: {fileID: -3044761870746976912, guid: b2751cc459567714d82b2122013de5d5, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: 
    speakerName: Adam
    portrait: {fileID: -3044761870746976912, guid: b2751cc459567714d82b2122013de5d5, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - No
    - Yes
    choiceMaps: 0a0000000b000000
    stat: 
    s1: -1
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: -1
    s2: 3
    l2: -200
    m2: 2.5
    k2: 0
  - text: Oh, um, sorry for wasting your time, sir.
    speakerName: Adam
    portrait: {fileID: -3044761870746976912, guid: b2751cc459567714d82b2122013de5d5, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Wow, really? Thank you so much... sire. I'll move in right away!
    speakerName: Adam
    portrait: {fileID: -3044761870746976912, guid: b2751cc459567714d82b2122013de5d5, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: Hi. I'm a representative of Sheepish Industries. In exchange for some workers
      and land, I could make you a small fortune.
    speakerName: Anish
    portrait: {fileID: -5950712953441586947, guid: 33c5b2627424cb743b93a740552a3419, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
    s1: 0
    l1: 0
    m1: 0
    k1: 0
    s2: 0
    l2: 0
    m2: 0
    k2: 0
  - text: 
    speakerName: Anish
    portrait: {fileID: -5950712953441586947, guid: 33c5b2627424cb743b93a740552a3419, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - No
    - Yes
    choiceMaps: 0e0000000f000000
    stat: 
